list/issues/8649", "content_rendered": "<p>今天才知道 Alist 也被卖了，好像还是和 HuTool 一个公司（贵州不够科技?）<br/>\n所以为啥不建议用 Fastjson 、HuTool 呢？<br/>\n因为对开发维护人员不信任！供应链投毒警告！<br/>\n国内基本没有啥开源氛围，即使是流行的开源项目（ Alist 有大约 50K star ），核心贡献者经常也就一两个人。<br/>\n随时都有突然搞个彩蛋、突然停止维护、突然被转卖、突然被植入恶意代码的风险，这谁受得了！  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/AlistGo/alist/issues/8649\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/AlistGo/alist/issues/8649</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1749629027, "replies": 67, "id": 1137946}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1727584731", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1727584731", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 43596, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1727584731", "stars": 6083, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 297854, "username": "bbroot", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bbroot", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f0b6c23d006e9840aff514318c0e915c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f0b6c23d006e9840aff514318c0e915c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f0b6c23d006e9840aff514318c0e915c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1520426125, "last_modified": 1717399678}, "last_reply_by": "silypie", "last_touched": 1749653677, "title": "大家小心谨慎使用 pdd 的以旧换新服务，有大坑", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1137810", "created": 1749606514, "deleted": 0, "content": "以旧换新，回收平台到手刀，新机默认激活不会给你退，pdd 官方不管，投诉最多给你个优惠券，最后相当于骗你买个新机....要不忍了到手刀，要不连以旧换新的补贴也没有，妥妥的诈骗", "content_rendered": "<p>以旧换新，回收平台到手刀，新机默认激活不会给你退，pdd 官方不管，投诉最多给你个优惠券，最后相当于骗你买个新机....要不忍了到手刀，要不连以旧换新的补贴也没有，妥妥的诈骗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1749606514, "replies": 64, "id": 1137810}, {"node": {"avatar_